Olisa Metuh in court today
ChannelsTV


Former spokesperson for the Peoples Democratic Party, Olisa Metuh, has been found guilty of three more counts on charges brought against him by the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission Metuh is standing trial in a N400m money laundering case. Justice Okon Abang of the Federal High Court, Abuja, is yet to give his final ruling on the matter. More to come...